=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Top Things to do in La Fortuna, Costa Rica!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/75831&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/07091541\/rio-celeste-waterefall-guide-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/07091541\/rio-celeste-waterefall-guide-1-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/07091541\/rio-celeste-waterefall-guide-1-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Rio Celeste Waterfalls, Costa Rica: The Ultimate Visitors Guide\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-rio-celeste-waterfalls\">Rio Celeste Waterfalls<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Rio Celeste Waterfalls are the main attraction in the Tenorio Volcano National Park. The water is fiercely blue &#x2013; almost bluer than the sky! <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"the-legend\">The Legend<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>An exciting legend gave the Rio its name (Rio Celeste means &#x2018;light blue river&#x2019;). The story goes that when God was creating the universe, he was painting the sky. When he finished, he washed the brushes in the river, creating the beautiful blue color that we see today at the Rio Celeste Waterfalls.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"Tenorio Volcano National Park costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Tenorio Volcano National Park costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-79455 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083514\/rio-celeste-8-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>However, in reality, it&#x2019;s an optical illusion caused by white minerals that coat the rocks underneath the water. The whiteness of the stones makes the Rio Celeste look far bluer than your average river!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Aside from the color, visiting the Rio Celeste Waterfalls is an impressive experience. At 98 feet high, watching the water plummet into the pool below is fantastic &#x2013; a reminder of how powerful nature is.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also visit:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/santa-teresa\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The beaches of Santa Teresa in Costa Rica<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"rio celeste waterfall costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rio celeste waterfall costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-79469 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083755\/rio-celeste-1-1-683x1024.jpg 68