r of the water.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79467 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083649\/rio-celeste-4-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\