\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083544\/rio-celeste-7.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-tips-for-rio-celeste-waterfalls\">Tips for Rio Celeste Waterfalls<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Rio Celeste Waterfalls hike can be a little bit challenging, so you&#x2019;ll need to wear good shoes, especially if it&#x2019;s muddy. The trail will be hard to walk in the rainy season, so it&#x2019;s essential to allocate extra time. If you don&#x2019;t have your hiking boots, you can rent them at the shop that&#x2019;s by the entrance for 5 USD.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Make sure to bring:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Water (refillable)<\/li><li>Snacks<\/li><li>Good shoes<\/li><li>Rain jacket<\/li><li>Mosquito repellent<\/li><li>Sunscreen&#xA0;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Reduce Plastic &amp; Travel Plastic-Free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"attractions\">Entrance Fee &amp; Opening Times<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Tickets cost 12 USD each (adult) and can be paid only by debit or credit card. It&#x2019;s impossible to buy tickets online before your visit, only when you reach the Tenorio Volcano National Park entrance. For this reason (especially in the busy Spring months), we recommend arriving as early as possible. The Tenorio Volcano National Park only allows a certain amount of people in the park each day, which means it&#x2019;s essential to arrive before the crowds.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Opening Times:<\/strong> 8 AM &#x2013; 4 PM (last entry at 2 PM). Make sure to arrive at the falls before 10 AM to see the area at its most peaceful. This might mean an early start, but it&#x2019;s so worth it!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-79461 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083559\/rio-celeste-5-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/07083